output.analysis:
Let me analyze this post according to the given criteria:
1. CMF Number: No CMF number is present, but this isn't mandatory for all posts.
2. Candidate Reference: - Directly refers to George Simion, who is a presidential candidate (Position 2) - The title "De ce e nevoie de George Simion PREŞEDINTE?" explicitly promotes him for the presidential position
3. Public Addressing: - The message clearly addresses the general public ("Românii au ocazia") - Paid advertisement with significant reach (45,000-50,000 impressions) - Published on multiple platforms (Facebook and Instagram)
4. Electoral Objective: - Clear electoral intent with the call for George Simion as president - Attempts to influence voters by suggesting a "unique chance" for change - Directly promotes a presidential candidate during the period when electoral propaganda is prohibited
5. Journalism vs Propaganda: - This is clearly not journalism but campaign material - Uses persuasive language rather than informative content - Presents a clear political agenda rather than objective information
6. Personal Opinion: - This is not a personal opinion but an organized campaign message - Paid advertisement from an official AUR party page - Structured political messaging
The timing of this post (after November 16, 2024) and its continuation during the propaganda prohibition period makes it particularly problematic.

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This constitutes electoral propaganda because: - Directly promotes a presidential candidate - Uses campaign messaging techniques - Is a paid advertisement reaching a large audience - Continues during the prohibition period - Has clear electoral objectives
conclusion.message-for-police: AUR - Sălașu de Sus, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin continuarea propagandei electorale după încheierea campaniei, manifestată prin publicarea și menținerea activă a unei reclame plătite pe Facebook (ID: 932890622061028) care promovează candidatul George Simion la funcția de președinte. Materialul, care a ajuns la 45.000-50.000 de afișări, reprezintă în mod clar propagandă electorală prin mesajul său explicit "De ce e nevoie de George Simion PREŞEDINTE?" și continuă să fie activ după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, încălcând astfel perioada de interdicție a propagandei electorale.
